---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="About China Unveiled - our mission to share authentic Chinese culture with the world.">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-stone-800 via-stone-900 to-red-950 text-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">About China Unveiled</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-stone-300">Bridging cultures through authentic storytelling.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-stone max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 mb-6">
          China Unveiled exists because the world knows China, but doesn't <em>understand</em> it. Stereotypes dominate—loud, garish, superficial. But behind the noise lies one of humanity's greatest civilizational achievements: 5,000 years of continuous culture, philosophy, art, and innovation.
        </p>
        <p class="text-stone-600 mb-6">
          We believe that understanding Chinese culture enriches everyone. Whether you're an international businessperson, a language student, a philosophy enthusiast, or simply curious—you deserve accurate, engaging, and respectful information about this remarkable civilization.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4 mt-10">What We Cover</h2>
        <ul class="text-stone-600 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>🍜 <strong>Food</strong> — The eight great cuisines, tea culture, and the philosophy of Chinese cooking</li>
          <li>📜 <strong>History</strong> — Dynasties, inventions, and the real stories behind China's rise</li>
          <li>👘 <strong>Clothing</strong> — Hanfu, silk, embroidery, and the aesthetics of traditional dress</li>
          <li>✒️ <strong>Poetry</strong> — Tang poetry, Song lyrics, and the art of calligraphy</li>
          <li>🥋 <strong>Martial Arts</strong> — Kung fu styles, Tai Chi, and Traditional Chinese Medicine</li>
          <li>☯️ <strong>Philosophy</strong> — Daoism, the Tao Te Ching, and ancient wisdom for modern life</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4 mt-10">Our Approach</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 mb-6">
          We write for curious minds, not specialists. Our articles are:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-stone-600 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>✅ <strong>Accurate</strong> — Based on primary sources and scholarly consensus</li>
          <li>✅ <strong>Accessible</strong> — Written for general audiences, not academic journals</li>
          <li>✅ <strong>Engaging</strong> — Stories, not lectures; discovery, not lecture</li>
          <li>✅ <strong>Respectful</strong> — No Orientalism, no condescension, no stereotypes</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4 mt-10">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600">
          Have a question, suggestion, or correction? We'd love to hear from you. Connect with us on social media or reach out via our newsletter.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
